#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/special_effects/halo.rst:71
msgid "Texture"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/special_effects/halo.rst:66
msgid ""
"Gives halo a texture. By default, textures are applied to objects with "
"Object coordinates and reflect on the halos by affecting their color, as "
"a whole, on the basis of the color of the vertex originating the halo. "
"Enable this feature to have the texture take effect *within* the halo, "
"and hence to have it with varying colors or transparencies; this will map"
" the whole texture to *every* halo. This technique proves very useful "
"when you want to create a realistic rain effect using particle systems, "
"or similar."
msgstr ""

